ich i charakterystycznych. Cz\u0119\u015b\u0107 2b, mezozoik/jura. Budowa Geologiczna Polski, 3.</ref><ref name=Spore6>Marcinkiewicz, T. (1974). Wyst\u0119powanie megaspor w obr\u0119bie zaburzonych warstw i liasu w profilu Koszalina. Geological Quarterly, 18(3), 595-601.</ref>\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n*''Biharisporites scaber''\n*''Biharisporites scabrus''\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n*Gorz\u00f3w\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\nMultiple Specimens.\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\nAffinities with the [[Lycopodiopsida]].\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n|-\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n[[Acanthotriletes]]<ref name=Spore2></ref><ref name=Spore3></ref><ref name=Spore4></ref><ref name=Spore5></ref><ref name=Spore6></ref>\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n*''Acanthotriletes trigonis''\n*''Acanthotriletes rarospinosus''\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n*Gorz\u00f3w\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\nMultiple Specimens.\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\nAffinities with the [[Lycophyta]].\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n|-\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n[[Eehitriletes]]<ref name=Spore2></ref><ref name=Spore3></ref><ref name=Spore4></ref><ref name=Spore5></ref><ref name=Spore6></ref>\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n*''Eehitriletes hispidus''\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n*Nearly all the formation\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\nMultiple Specimens.\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\nAffinities with the [[Lycophyta]].\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n|-\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n[[Hughesisporites]]<ref name=Spore2></ref><ref name=Spore3></ref><ref name=Spore4></ref><ref name=Spore5></ref><ref name=Spore6></ref>\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n*''Hughesisporites stillarus''\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n*Various\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\nMultiple Specimens.\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\nAffinities with the [[Lycophyta]].\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n|-\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n[[