ites variegatus''\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n*Various\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\nMultiple Specimens.\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\nAffinities with the [[Pteridopsida]].\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n|-\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n[[Leiotriletes]]<ref name=Spore2></ref><ref name=Spore3></ref><ref name=Spore4></ref><ref name=Spore5></ref><ref name=Spore6></ref>\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n*''Leiotriletes mecklenburgensis''\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n*Various\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\nMultiple Specimens.\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\nAffinities with the [[Pteridopsida]].\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n|-\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n[[Gleicheniidites]]<ref name=Spore2></ref><ref name=Spore3></ref><ref name=Spore4></ref><ref name=Spore5></ref><ref name=Spore6></ref>\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n*''Gleicheniidites carinatus''\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n*Various\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\nMultiple Specimens.\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\nAffinities with the [[Gleicheniaceae]].\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n|-\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n[[Marattisporites]]<ref name=Spore2></ref><ref name=Spore3></ref><ref name=Spore4></ref><ref name=Spore5></ref><ref name=Spore6></ref>\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n*''Marattisporites scabratus''\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n*Various\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\nMultiple Specimens.\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\nAffinities with the [[Marattiaceae]].\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n|-\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n[[Matonisporites]]<ref name=Spore2></ref><ref name=Spore3></ref><ref name=Spore4></ref><ref name=Spore5></ref><ref name=Spore6></ref>\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n*''Matonisporites phlebopteroides''\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\n*Various\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\nMultiple Specimens.\n|style=\"background:#D1FFCF;\" |\nAffinities with the [[Matoniaceae]].\n|style=\"background