ries\n|\nSeveral Specimens\n|\nA [[Neuroptera]]n of the family [[Prohemerobiidae]].\n|\n[[File:1er Congr\u00e8s international d'entomologie, Bruxelles, 1-6 ao\u00fbt, 1910 (1911-12) (16041759264).jpg|thumb|center|225px|''[[Prohemerobius]]'' at the bottom]]\n|-\n|\n[[Mesosmylina]]\n|\n*''Mesosmylina falcifera''\n|\n* Green Series\n|\nSeveral Specimens\n|\nA [[Neuroptera]]n of the family [[Osmylidae]].\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Polyosmylus]]\n|\n*''Polyosmylus excelsus''\n|\n* Green Series\n|\nSeveral Specimens\n|\nA [[Neuroptera]]n.\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Mesoleon]]\n|\n*''Mesoleon dobbertinianus''\n|\n* Green Series\n|\nSeveral Specimens\n|\nA [[Neuroptera]]n.\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Loxophleps]]\n|\n*''Loxophleps costalis''\n|\n* Green Series\n|\nSeveral Specimens\n|\nA [[Neuroptera]]n.\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Melaneimon]]\n|\n*''Melaneimon dubium''\n|\n* Green Series\n|\nSeveral Specimens\n|\nA [[Neuroptera]]n.\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Melamnous]]\n|\n*''Melamnous indistinctus''\n|\n* Green Series\n|\nSeveral Specimens\n|\nA [[Neuroptera]]n.\n|\n|- \n|\n[[ Solenoptilon]]\n|\n*''Solenoptilon kochi''\n|\n* Green Series\n|\nSeveral Specimens\n|\nA [[Neuroptera]]n of the Family [[Solenoptilidae]].\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Epigambria]]\n|\n*''Epigambria longipennis''\n|\n* Green Series\n|\nSeveral Specimens\n|\nA [[Neuroptera]]n of the Family [[Epigambriidae]].\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Apeirophlebia]]\n|\n*''Apeirophlebia grandis''\n|\n* Green Series\n|\nSeveral Specimens\n|\nA [[Neuroptera]]n of the Family [[Psychopsidae]]. An unexpectec giant Silky lacewing, with a size up to 7 cm.\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Magnasupplephlebia]]<ref>W. Zessin. 1982. Durchsicht einiger liassischer Odonatopteroida unter Ber\u00fccksichtigung neuer Funde von Dobbertin in Mecklenburg. Deutsche Entomologische Zeitschrift 29:101-106</ref><ref>Zessin, W., & Ansorge, J. (1987). Magnasupplephlebia intercalaria n. sp.\u2010eine neue Anisozygopterenart aus dem oberen Lias von Mitteleuropa.(Insecta, Odonata). Deutsche Entomologische Zeitschrift, 34(4\u20105), 383-386.</ref>\n|\n*''Magnasu