um frechi''\n*''Parnidium geinitzi''\n|\n* Green Series\n|\nSeveral Specimens\n|\nA [[Coleoptera]]n.\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Polypamon]]\n|\n*''Polypamon byrrhoides''\n|\n* Green Series\n|\nSeveral Specimens\n|\nA [[Coleoptera]]n.\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Bathygerus]]\n|\n*''Bathygerus bellus''\n*''Bathygerus divergens''\n|\n* Green Series\n|\nSeveral Specimens\n|\nA [[Coleoptera]]n.\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Plastonebria]]\n|\n*''Plastonebria scudderi''\n|\n* Green Series\n|\nSeveral Specimens\n|\nA [[Coleoptera]]n.\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Plastobuprestites]]\n|\n*''Plastobuprestites elegans''\n|\n* Green Series\n|\nSeveral Specimens\n|\nA [[Coleoptera]]n.\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Nannoodes]]\n|\n*''Nannoodes pseudocistela''\n|\n* Green Series\n|\nSeveral Specimens\n|\nA [[Coleoptera]]n.\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Pseudocyphon]]\n|\n*''Pseudocyphon geinitzi''\n|\n* Green Series\n|\nSeveral Specimens\n|\nA [[Coleoptera]]n.\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Keleusticus]]\n|\n*''Keleusticus zirkeli''\n|\n* Green Series\n|\nSeveral Specimens\n|\nA [[Coleoptera]]n.\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Allognosis]]\n|\n*''Allognosis nitens''\n|\n* Green Series\n|\nSeveral Specimens\n|\nA [[Coleoptera]]n.\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Enamma]]\n|\n*''Enamma striatum''\n|\n* Green Series\n|\nSeveral Specimens\n|\nA [[Coleoptera]]n.\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Pseudoprionites]]\n|\n*''Pseudoprionites liasinus''\n|\n* Green Series\n|\nSeveral Specimens\n|\nA [[Coleoptera]]n.\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Nebrioides]]\n|\n*''Nebrioides dobbertinensis''\n|\n* Green Series\n|\nSeveral Specimens\n|\nA [[Coleoptera]]n.\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Paracurculium]]\n|\n*''Paracurculium punctatum''\n|\n* Green Series\n|\nSeveral Specimens\n|\nA [[Coleoptera]]n.\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Apioderes]]\n|\n*''Apioderes punctatus''\n|\n* Green Series\n|\nSeveral Specimens\n|\nA [[Coleoptera]]n.\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Apioderes]]\n|\n*''Apioderes punctatus''\n|\n* Green Series\n|\nSeveral Specimens\n|\nA [[Coleoptera]]n.\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Bareus]]\n|\n*''Bareus strigipennis''\n|\n* Green Series\n|\nSeveral Specimens\n|\nA [[Coleoptera]]n.\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Anypostatus]]\n|\n*''Anypostatus taurus''\n|